<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="contrary-adj">contrary <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒntrəri/    美 /'kɑːntreri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>相反的；相对的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a contrary opinion
持相反意见</p></div>

<ul>
<li>(be) contrary to:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Contrary to popular belief, many cats dislike milk.
与普遍的看法相反，许多猫并不喜欢牛奶。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The results were contrary to my expectation.
结果与我的预期相反。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>He seems to be giving the impression that he didn’t enjoy himself in Paris. <strong><em>_</em></strong>_(正相反) he had a wonderful time.   （2012 江西改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. On the contrary  </p></div>